# 📊 Sales Data Analysis using Python

## 📖 Project Overview
This project analyzes sales data using Python to identify sales trends, top-performing products, and business insights through data cleaning, exploratory data analysis (EDA), and visualization.

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Jupyter Notebook

## 🎯 Objectives
- Clean the dataset
- Analyze sales trends
- Identify top-selling products
- Create visualizations
- Generate business insights

## 📈 Key Features
- Data Cleaning
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Data Visualization
- Sales Trend Analysis

## 📂 Files
- `sales-data-analysis-python.ipynb` – Jupyter Notebook
- `README.md` – Project documentation

